.TH AUTOM8 1 "December 2025" "Autom8 1.0.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
autom8 \- Enterprise Systems Automation Platform
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B autom8
[\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR]
[\fB\-v\fR|\fB\-\-version\fR]
.IR command
[\fIoptions\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B autom8
is a production-grade automation platform for modern systems engineering.
It provides RESTful API services, background task scheduling, and comprehensive
system monitoring capabilities.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-h ", " \-\-help
Display help information and exit.
.TP
.BR \-v ", " \-\-version
Display version information and exit.
.SH COMMANDS
.SS Service Management
.TP
.B api start
Start the API server
.TP
.B api stop
Stop the API server
.TP
.B api restart
Restart the API server
.TP
.B api status
Check API server status
.TP
.B scheduler start
Start the background scheduler
.TP
.B scheduler stop
Stop the background scheduler
.TP
.B scheduler status
Check scheduler status
.SS Database Operations
.TP
.B db init
Initialize the database schema
.TP
.B db migrate
Run database migrations
.TP
.B db seed
Seed database with test data
.TP
.B db shell
Open interactive database shell
.TP
.B db backup
Create database backup
.TP
.B db restore \fIfile\fR
Restore database from backup file
.SS System Operations
.TP
.B health
Perform system health check
.TP
.B info
Display system information
.TP
.B metrics
Show system metrics
.TP
.B logs [\fB\-\-tail\fR \fIN\fR]
Display application logs (optionally tail last N lines)
.SS Testing
.TP
.B test [\fB\-\-coverage\fR]
Run test suite with optional coverage report
.TP
.B test unit
Run unit tests only
.TP
.B test integration
Run integration tests only
.SS Development
.TP
.B dev setup
Setup development environment
.TP
.B dev lint
Run code linters
.TP
.B dev format
Format code with Black
.SS Contact Management
.TP
.B contacts list
List all contacts
.TP
.B contacts add
Add new contact (interactive)
.TP
.B contacts delete \fIid\fR
Delete contact by ID
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
Start the API server:
.B autom8 api start
.TP
Check system health:
.B autom8 health
.TP
Run tests with coverage:
.B autom8 test \-\-coverage
.TP
Backup database:
.B autom8 db backup
.TP
View last 100 log lines:
.B autom8 logs \-\-tail 100
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.autom8/config
User configuration file
.TP
.I /etc/autom8/autom8.conf
System-wide configuration file
.TP
.I /var/log/autom8/app.log
Application log file
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
.B AUTOM8_CONFIG
Path to configuration file
.TP
.B AUTOM8_LOG_LEVEL
Logging level (DEBUG, INFO, WARNING, ERROR, CRITICAL)
.TP
.B DATABASE_URL
Database connection string
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Success
.TP
.B 1
General error
.TP
.B 2
Command not found
.TP
.B 3
Invalid arguments
.SH SECURITY
Autom8 implements enterprise-grade security features including:
.IP \(bu 2
JWT-based authentication
.IP \(bu 2
AES-256 field-level encryption
.IP \(bu 2
Rate limiting (200 req/min default)
.IP \(bu 2
Security headers (HSTS, CSP)
.IP \(bu 2
Input validation and sanitization
